             regularly recurring events is completed. <br>
         (1b)A complete set of such events.<br>
<br>
  The cycle is a series of events ie. A Unique Monster Spawn which is triggered by the death of a previous monster. <br>
<br>
  In the case of Frontier Mountains that cycle is Three monsters linked but in opposite corners of the zone so that when one monster dies it triggers the spawn of the next monster in the cycle.<br>
<br>
