t of the Cenobite a 7 wisdom cleric only belt or the Dustcryers Crystal Ball a 2 Intelligence 30 mana item that fits into your ranged slot. <br>
<br>
And the Cycle is quite fun due to its fast pace. The distances between spawns the somewhat difficult terrain and of course all the aggro mobs that wander around in between the Unique mobs enhance the ... excitement :)<br>
<br>
In my opinion one of the good things Verant introduced into the game with Kunark there are similar cycles in Skyfire and Trakanon<br>
