   When I was around level 54 I would use Form of the Howler<br>
  (2/tick mana regen isn't much but better than nothing), ES<br>
  Vambs and Lumi Staff (for backup, long casting time on the<br>
  staff doesn't make it too useful here) and solo'd the Blutigin<br>
  cycle. Usually binding near the goblin spawn point. The<br>
  biggest pain in doing this is other people lurking near the<br>
  goblin spawn. I've gated and hit track just in time to see<br>
  Blutigin drop off. Word of advice, unless you have a tracker<br>
  who can sit at this spawn point don't bother doing the<br>
  cycle if you see other high level people in the zone.<br>
